a-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">watchOS 10</a> 。而现在，这可以说是阵容中的最佳价值。虽然第二代 Apple Watch SE 的价格更低，为 249 美元，但差距很小，值得为 8 的常亮显示屏和更先进的健康传感器多花钱。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的技术交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-8-is-back-on-sale-for-329-141547847.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-8-is-back-on-sale-for-329-141547847.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6da7c27b-31f7-4cbe-ae53-48ab3bea9800</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 19 Jun 2023 14:15:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687184148</ingested><modified> 2023-06-19T14:15:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/398c6da0-ee67-11ed-bfa7-872a4ff5351c" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="